config.script:
try:

		selecteWo=self.getSibling("Table_WOClubb").props.data			
		woCount=selecteWo.getRowCount()
		woNo=[]
		parameters=[]
		workFlowId=[]
		notValild=0	
		for i in range(woCount):
			ischecked=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'ViewDetails')
			Wostatus=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WOStatus')
			system.perspective.print("ischecked-->"+str(ischecked))
			system.perspective.print("Wostatus-->"+str(Wostatus))
			if ischecked=='true' :
				if Wostatus!='In-Progress':
					woNo1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WONo')
					workflowId1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WorkFlowId')
					lineId1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'LineId')
					paralist={"WONO":woNo1,"workflowId":workflowId1,"lineId1":lineId1}
					woNo.append(woNo1)
					parameters.append(paralist)
					system.perspective.print("parameters Doct-->"+str(parameters))
					self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").meta.visible=0
					self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text=''
					notValild=0
				else:
					self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").meta.visible=1
					self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text='The selected workorder already is in progress.'
					notValild=1
					break
		if notValild==0:
			if woNo!=[]:		
				system.perspective.openPopup('StartOpPopup','Project_MES_Solution/ProductionOperatorConsole/PopUps/WOClubing/PopupClubStartOP',params = {'woNo':woNo,'parameters':parameters},draggable=False,resizable = False,modal=True,showCloseIcon=False)		
			else:
				self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text='Please select the workorders to Start'
		else:
			pass

	except:
		system.perspective.print("Exception::WO Start")
		exc_type, exc_obj,tb = sys.exc_info()
		errorMessage = "Error:"+ str(exc_obj)
		system.perspective.print(errorMessage)
		lineno = tb.tb_lineno
		system.perspective.print(lineno)

selecteWo=self.getSibling("Table_WOClubb").props.data			
	woCount=selecteWo.getRowCount()
	woNo=[]
	parameters=[]
	workFlowId=[]	
	notValild=0
	for i in range(woCount):
		ischecked=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'ViewDetails')
		Wostatus=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WOStatus')
#		system.perspective.print("ischecked-->"+str(ischecked))
#		system.perspective.print("Wostatus-->"+str(Wostatus))
		if ischecked=='true' :
			if Wostatus!='On-Hold':
				woNo1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WONo')
				workflowId1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'WorkFlowId')
				lineId1=selecteWo.getValueAt(i, 'LineId')
				paralist={"WONO":woNo1,"workflowId":workflowId1,"lineId":lineId1}
				woNo.append(woNo1)
				parameters.append(paralist)
				system.perspective.print("parameters Doct-->"+str(parameters))
				self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").meta.visible=0
				self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text=''
				notValild=0
			else:
				self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").meta.visible=1
				self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text='The selected workorder is already On-Hold.'
				notValild=1
				break	
	if notValild==0 :
		if parameters!=[]:		
			system.perspective.openPopup('HoldPopup','Project_MES_Solution/ProductionOperatorConsole/PopUps/WOClubing/ConfirmationClubHold',params = {'Parameters':parameters},draggable=False,resizable = False,modal=True,showCloseIcon=False)
		else:
			self.getSibling("LblValidationMessage").props.text='Please select the workorders to Hold'
	else:
		pass
